Text:
Thanks for the upload!

Still, I hate this book. Ayn Rand was an AWFUL writer; her books are about as interesting as her psuedo-philosophy "Objectivism". LOL.

Ayn Rand did not write her philosophical novels for lol9765's amusement - you'll find plenty of lols elsewhere.

If you want to criticize her ideas (as I do), please be diligent and back your arguments with serious essays.
